OL,3,CTwo men jailed after boarding plane
OL,4,Cdrunk and verbally abusing cabin crew
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed after they
OL,7,Fhad to be taken off a plane because
OL,8,Fthey were drunk.
OL,10,FJoshua Stone, 32, and Ryan Sanders,
OL,11,F34, were verbally abusive to EasyJet
OL,12,Fcabin crew ahead of their flight from
OL,13,FBristol Airport on the evening of 11
OL,14,FJuly 2023.
OL,16,FThe pair were warned about their
OL,17,Fbehaviour but continued to be abusive
OL,18,Fso they were escorted off the plane.
