OL,3,CTwo men jailed after boarding plane
OL,4,Cdrunk and verbally abusing cabin crew
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police officers
OL,7,Fcharged Stone and Sanders with
OL,8,Fentering an aircraft drunk.
OL,10,FDuring police interview Sanders said
OL,11,Fhe had consumed cider, lager and a
OL,12,FMalibu and coke, but denied he was
OL,13,Fdrunk.
OL,15,FStone was also charged with entering a
OL,16,Fsecurity restricted area without
OL,17,Fpermission after he tried to getaway
OL,18,Ffrom security.
