OL,3,CTwo men jailed after boarding plane
OL,4,Cdrunk and verbally abusing cabin crew
OL,6,FBoth men pleaded guilty to the
OL,7,Fcharges. Sanders, of Southmead Road in
OL,8,FFilton, was jailed for 14 weeks.
OL,10,FStone, of Greystoke Avenue in
OL,11,FSouthmead, received a 25-week
OL,12,Fsentence.JSergeant Rachael Hodges
OL,13,Fsaid: "The last thing we want to do is
OL,14,Fto stop people who want to have a good
OL,15,Ftime and relax before going on
OL,16,Fholiday.J"These two men's drunken and
OL,17,Fobnoxious behaviour saw them be
OL,18,Fabusive to cabin crew and led to
OL,19,Fconcerns they could represent a
OL,20,Fsecurity risk had the flight taken off.
